Comment: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:06.92,OP-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,It's TRUE FOOL LOVE! Hold me tight!
Comment: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.26,OP-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,拿出你的勇气  MY DARLING
Comment: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:12.10,OP-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,今后也许不会都是欢声笑语
Comment: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.85,OP-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,要靠我们的努力
Comment: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.39,OP-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,ONCE MORE SMILE, TWICE MORE CHIME
Comment: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:19.27,OP-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,快看向这边 darling
Comment: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:28.78,OP-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,察觉到我的脉脉情意
Comment: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:01.50,insert-JP,,0,0,0,,--------------------插入曲---------------------
Comment: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:39.86,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,たぶん　気づいていた
Comment: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:47.09,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,キミの　やさしさに
Comment: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:53.99,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,きっと　甘えてた
Comment: 0,0:16:53.99,0:17:00.88,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,恋しく　なるほど
Comment: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:39.86,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,我终于注意到了
Comment: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:47.09,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,你的温柔
Comment: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:53.99,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定是被你宠坏了
Comment: 0,0:16:53.99,0:17:00.88,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,这样神魂颠倒
Comment: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:04.78,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,痛いくらい
Comment: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:08.30,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,鼓動が強く
Comment: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:14.87,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,鳴り響くよ
Comment: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:22.86,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,そっと開くココロ　流れて
Comment: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:30.56,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,パッと開く夜空　ほっぺ照らす花火
Comment: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:37.57,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,音に紛れ　重ねた手　願うように
Comment: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:44.41,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,今が　続けば　いいのにな
Comment: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:51.85,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,音に紛れ　ひとりごと　こぼすように
Comment: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:58.69,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,「好き」と　言えたら　いいのにな
Comment: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:09.21,insert-JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,終わったあともキレイ…
Comment: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:04.78,insert-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,仿佛在诉说疼痛
Comment: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:08.30,insert-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,怦怦心跳
Comment: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:14.87,insert-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,鼓噪着
Comment: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:22.86,insert-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,悄然敞开的真心 任其流淌
Comment: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:30.56,insert-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,突然绽放的夜空 烟火照亮了脸颊
Comment: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:37.57,insert-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,响声掩盖下 我多想紧握你的手
Comment: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:44.41,insert-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,此刻若是永远持续就好了
Comment: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:51.85,insert-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,响声掩盖下 我多想放下顾虑
Comment: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:58.69,insert-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,若能说出「喜欢你」就好了
Comment: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:09.21,insert-CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,过后的夜空会更美吗…
Comment: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:09.21,insert-CN,,0,0,0,,---------------------------插入曲结束----------------------------------
